     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">a) 4 cities (Bangalore, Mumbai, Bhubaneshwar and Hyderabad) created a cadre of trainers under the partnership of UNDP and NIMHANS to deliver e-learning modules
b) 5 state governments supported in delivery of welfare schemes
c) 120 community cadres created
d) 70, 876 migrant households benefit
e) 10,026 household assessments conducted
f) 2 impact assessments prepared
g) Regional workshops have been postponed due to challenges posed by COVID-19
h) National consultation has been postponed due to challenges posed by COVID-19</narrative>
